* Raoul Graumont. &quot;Handbook of Knots&quot;. Cornell Maritime Press/Tidewater Publishers. .
* R.S. Lee. &quot;All The Knots You Need&quot;. Algrove Publishing. .
* Allen Padgett and Bruce Smith. &quot;On Rope&quot;. National Speleological Society. .
